Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:47.39,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Love，I've got to feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:50.66,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}If you put your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:54.05,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I know what my life would be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:59.10,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Oh，you are all I ever need
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:04.69,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I try to hear what you say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:06.93,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}So I pray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:10.72,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}But you're fading away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:17.95,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Don't go and break my fragile heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:21.43,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}We won't fall apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:29.36,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}'Cause you're my only star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:35.12,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I wonder why my tears come at night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:38.65,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Calling you，so like a little child
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:42.07,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}All the things you have in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:45.21,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I wish I could see your insides
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:48.28,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}My love，you've got to feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:51.77,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And if we put our trust in you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:55.24,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}You know what our lives would be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:02:02.65,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Oh，you are the one I believe
